有行政区均维持发布「风雨预警」信号，其中除花都、从化、白云、荔湾发布暴雨黄色预警信号外，其余各区均发布暴雨橙色预警信号；除从化发布雷雨大风橙色预警信号外，广州其余各区均发布雷雨大风黄色预警信号。广州市气象台提醒市民及有关职能部门，继续做好防御工作。广州塔 1 小时内 6 次接闪，21 日早上可能又有大雨 __ 新快网广东多地暴雨 积水没脖行人推车前行 大哥淡定推车十分稳！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-1180665869be6022010c62500f828b3a_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "282 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653629450"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIzIe09Lz+w7FuEAMaCTEwNzUyODg1MyCg55GxBjAAOLMBQAFyCTY1MzYyOTQ1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1713690523.454525", "card_id": "Q_653620617", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 110}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国众议院投票批准向乌克兰提供超 600 亿美元援助，此举会对俄乌局势带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "（央视网）据美国《国会山报》报道，当地时间 4 月 20 日，美国众议院以 311 票赞成、 112 票反对、 1 票弃权的投票结果，通过了一项价值 950 亿美元对外援助法案中的涉乌部分。这部分法案将向乌克兰提供超过 600 亿美元的援助。 美众议院议员：对以色列军援「可能导致更多平民被杀」美国众议院投票批准向乌克兰提供超 600 亿美元援助"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-153950b08fa05a61a51c19b2209116ea_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "216 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653620617"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIzIe09Lz+w7FuEAMaCTEwNzUyNjkwNSDDo5GxBjAAOLYBQAJyCTY1MzYyMDYxN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1713690523.455166", "card_id": "Q_653309965", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52